  "text": "Dietary fiber helps to prevent the risks of chronic diseases such as cancer, cardiovascular diseases, and diabetes mellitus. It also prevents constipation by enhancing water absorption in the colon and inhibits cholesterol synthesis [CITATION_1] . Therefore, consumption of bara will have these health benefits.",
